    "reasoning": "Let me now check the 2024 10-K for the global ARPU numbers more carefully - the backlinko page says $17.26 for UCAN in 2024, but the SEC filing says $17.20. Let me verify with the actual filing.\n\nThe 2024 10-K (which is the most authoritative source) says:\n- Global: 2024: $11.70, 2023: $11.64, 2022: $11.76\n- UCAN: 2024: $17.20, 2023: $16.28, 2022: $15.86\n- EMEA: 2024: $10.96, 2023: $10.87, 2022: $10.99\n- LATAM: 2024: $8.24, 2023: $8.66, 2022: $8.48\n- APAC: 2024: $7.29, 2023: $7.64, 2022: $8.50\n\nThe 2019 10-K says:\n- Global: 2019: $10.82\n- UCAN: 2019: $12.57\n- EMEA: 2019: $10.33\n- LATAM: 2019: $8.21\n- APAC: 2019: $9.24\n\nSo there's a discrepancy for UCAN 2024: backlinko says $17.26, SEC filing says $17.20. Let me use the SEC filing data since these are official company filings.\n\nLet me also look at the 2020, 2021, 2022, and 2023 10-Ks to fill in the gaps for 2020 and 2021.",
